trans-unit.source: Provides collection support for a collection of document pages.
trans-unit.target: 提供文件頁面集合的集合支援。

trans-unit.source: Adds a new page to the page collection.
trans-unit.target: 將新頁面加入至頁面集合。

trans-unit.source: The new page to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: 要加入至集合的新頁面。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index within the collection where the page was added.
trans-unit.target: 將頁面加入的集合中以零為起始的索引。

trans-unit.source: newPageContent was passed as .
The page passed as newPageContent already existed in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 當做網頁傳遞 newPageContent 已經存在於集合中。

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of elements contained in the page collection.
trans-unit.target: 取得頁面集合中包含的元素數目。

trans-unit.source: The number of elements in the collection.
Returns an enumerator for iterating through the page collection.
trans-unit.target: 傳回逐一查看頁面集合的列舉值。

trans-unit.source: Enumerators only allow reading the data in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 列舉值只允許讀取集合中的資料。

trans-unit.source: Enumerators cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: 列舉值無法用於修改基礎集合。

trans-unit.source: See <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>.<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable.GetEnumerator%2A> for other remarks about how enumerators should be used.
trans-unit.target: 請參閱<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>。<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable.GetEnumerator%2A>的列舉值的使用方式的其他備註。</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable.GetEnumerator%2A> </xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>

trans-unit.source: An enumerator that can be used to iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: 可用來逐一查看集合的列舉值。

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.PageContent"></xref> element at the specified index within the collection.
trans-unit.target: 取得<xref href="System.Windows.Documents.PageContent"></xref>集合內指定索引處的項目。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the page to get.
trans-unit.target: 要取得之頁面的以零為起始的索引。

trans-unit.source: The page content element at the specified index within the collection.
trans-unit.target: 集合中指定的索引處的頁面內容的元素。

trans-unit.source: This member supports the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winfx](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] infrastructure and is not intended to be used directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: 此成員支援[!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winfx](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]基礎結構，不適合直接從您的程式碼使用。
